              "free_text": [
                "",
                "Stack target technique",
                "deuteron energy:21 MeV.",
                "beam intensity: 300 nA.",
                "The charge was measured in a Faraday-cup type target",
                "holder.",
                "The energy degradation was calculated by using the",
                "semi empirical formula of Andersen and Ziegler (1977).",
                "Decay data were taken from NUDAT (Kinsey et al 1997).",
                "Samples and monitor foils were measured",
